title: Alex Jones Show 2009.03.10
description:
Tue Mar 10 2009

48 kbps - volume adjusted

 	

Alex welcomes back Dr. Ron Paul to talk about the "stimulus" bill. 

Additional guests include 
Terry Bressi of Checkpoint USA, a website dedicated to exposing the proliferation of suspicionless checkpoints in America, 
Webster Tarpley, author of Obama - The Postmodern Coup, 
Ches Cain of Project Liberty AM, the radio transmitter initiative dedicated to spreading the word, and 
Keith Byrne of We Are Change Ireland who will talk about the killing of two British soldiers.
